Dropped by after the recommendation of a friend and was very pleased! Be prepared to wait a little for the food since they do make things as they are ordered. A small inconvenience for fresh food. Definitely recommend the lunch special which is available on Thursdays and Fridays. Lunch special includes 1 meat and 2 sides for $8. Also, be sure to check their business hours as their hours seem to vary from time to time. Lastly, there isn't much seating inside but there are a few additional tables under the patio outside. Glad to see black owned small businesses like this one doing well!

Delicious food!!!!  Okay service. I can't say enough about their BBQ.  We used them to cater an adult birthday party and EVERYONE raved about the food. We ordered ribs, smoked chicken wings, chopped chicken and sausage all cooked to perfection. My only complaint is that they were late and made no effort to remedy it. It's a contract not a hookup and that goes both ways if my money is green and delivered on time, I expect full professionalism. I understand things happen especially when cooking but offer some remedy for me having to leave a house full of guests to pick up late food.   Other than that fantastic.
